name: Small Tree Branch
description: It's the branch of a tree but it's so small it may as well be called a stick.

name: Iron Sword
description: A simple sword made out of iron. Looks way too average.

name: Iron Lance
description: A lance from a fallen average knight, it's really long, thought it doesn't matter here.

name: Knight Shield
description: It's a shield with the knights order's symbol, it was probably left behind by one of the knights while running way.

name: Magic Wand
description: A magic stick that seems to release sparkles, pretty good for new years.

name: Musamara
description: A long black saber that may or may not unleash its power later.

name: Bloodthirster
description: A scary looking blade that looks like is going to eat you at any time.

name: Vampiric FANgs
description: A fan with fangs covered on fresh blood, looks like it ate not too long ago.

name: Careless Whisper
description: As the silence dies, something in your eyes calls to mind a silver blade and all its sad good-byes.

name: Excalibur
description: The legendary sword of a legendary king from a legendary legend. But what is it doing here?

name: Ear Cutter
description: They are just too long.

name: Low Lander
description: A magic spell that excels at hitting close to the ground!

name: Globlin Slayer
description: The blunt sword of an obsessive hunter. They'll never come out of their holes.

name: Holy Light
description: It's just a flashlight, but holy God it hurts the eyes.

name: Falchion
description: Even thought it's also known as the Dragon's Bane, it has killed more Humans than Dragons.

name: Phantom Dancer
description: Even ghosts will be scared of your fantastic moves.

name: Pea Shooter
description: A spell that shoots small peas like bullets. Maybe with the sunlight they would be bigger.

name: Diamond Pickaxe
description: You would probably get more out of this by selling it.

name: Lumberjack's Axe
description: You can hear a girl... and she sounds pretty arrogant, you better not throw this axe, no you are not crazy yet.

name: Engulfing Lightning
description: Originally it could cut islands in half, but nothing is eternal.

name: Durability Test Weapon
description: This is a weapon made to test the durability system.
